Process called "add_method_to_table" that takes method as JuliaMethod, ctx as JuliaSemanticContext returns Nothing:
    Note: Add method to the global method table

    Let func_name be method.name
    If not ctx.method_table contains key func_name:
        Set ctx.method_table at key func_name to a list containing nothing
    End If

    Let method_list be ctx.method_table at key func_name
    Add method to end of method_list
    Set ctx.method_table at key func_name to method_list
End Process

Process called "validate_julia_semantics" that takes ctx as JuliaSemanticContext returns Nothing:
    Note: Perform final semantic validation

    @Reasoning:
    Final validation checks for Julia-specific issues such as method
    ambiguities, type stability problems, performance issues, and
    module dependency problems.
    @End Reasoning

    Call validate_julia_method_table with ctx
    Call validate_julia_type_definitions with ctx
    Call validate_julia_module_dependencies with ctx
    Call validate_julia_performance_annotations with ctx
    Call validate_julia_type_stability with ctx
End Process

